custom_fields.assessment_structure:
This is a pass / fail course. The final grade will be based on:
1)	attending and participating in the beginning of semester meeting [mandatory];
2)	successful teaching of the assigned StuCo course on the day/time that is scheduled;
3)	submitting mid-term and final grades on time, as instructed by StuCo course administrator Kristin Lavery;
4)	responding to any and all inquiries made about the StuCo course.
